Doordarshan recently shared a poll on Ramayan which reads - For whom did Hanuman bring Sanjeevani Booti? It may sound like the simplest and easiest question but what's interesting here is the options: Sugreev, Lakshman and Shatrughan.Netizens are having a field day commenting on the poll options. Did DD just troll Sonakshi Sinha and put Shatrughan’s (Sonakshi’s father) name on purpose.Let us refresh your memory.This will instantly take you back to one of the episodes from Kaun Banega Crorepati 11, where Sonakshi Sinha as a guest had to face the same question. She used a lifeline to answer and later was brutally trolled on social media.In the episode, even Amitabh Bachchan was dumbfound and requested her mom Poonam to not show the episode to her father. For the uninitiated, Sonakshi's father’s name is Shatrughan Sinha , her brothers' names are Luv and Kush and her uncles' names are Lakshman, Bharat and Ram. Even the bunglow she lives in is named Ramayana.Now take a look at some of the hilarious responses from Twitter after Ramayan’s re-run show started airing and also DD’s poll on Twitter.Most of the netizens are convinced that the question is hinted at Sonakshi.
